<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=windows-1252">
<title>William Grant Still, African American Composer, Arranger & Oboist</title>
<meta name="keywords" content="African American Symphony, African American composer, African American arranger, African American oboist, African American conductor, operas, symphonies, ballets, piano works">
<meta name="description" content="William Grant Still (1895-1978) was an African American composer, jazz arranger, oboist and conductor. His &quot;Afro-American Symphony&quot; is one of the best known symphonies by a Black composer, and established him as a major composer. Stil's 150 classical works included five symphonies, four ballets and nine operas. Among the many recordings of the &quot;Afro-American Symphony&quot; is Chandos 9154 (1993) by the Detroit Symphony Orchestra under Neeme Järvi, Conductor.">
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 6.0">
<meta name="ProgId" content="FrontPage.Editor.Document">
<meta name="Microsoft Theme" content="none">
</head>

